{"id":199557,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/global-voices-瓜地马拉：线上纪录片透过幸存者的证词来界/","date":"2011-12-02T15:01:19Z","modified":"2011-12-02T15:01:19Z","title":"Global Voices | 瓜地马拉：线上纪录片透过幸存者的证词来界定种族屠杀","content":"<p><p>迈可<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://centralamericanpolitics.blogspot.com/2011/11/new-genocide-video-about-guatemala.html\" href=\"http://centralamericanpolitics.blogspot.com/2011/11/new-genocide-video-about-guatemala.html\">分享了</a>《我们的声音、我们的记忆：瓜地马拉的种族屠杀 》这支西班牙语纪录片，<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x5-JZPSGnCo&#038;feature=player_embedded#!\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x5-JZPSGnCo&#038;feature=player_embedded#%21\">本片的完整内容可以在YouTube</a>观赏。他进一步说明：“这支纪录片[略]采用了幸存者与专家的证词来阐述种族屠杀的概念，并以此论证瓜国军方对马雅原住民社群所犯下的暴行，符合<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.hrweb.org/legal/genocide.html\" href=\"http://www.hrweb.org/legal/genocide.html\">国际法所界定的种族屠杀</a>。”</p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/silvia-vinas/\" title=\"文章导读 Silvia Viñas\">Silvia Viñas</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/shanta/\" title=\"文章导读 Shanta\">Shanta</a></span></span><br />\n · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/11/28/guatemala-survivors-testimonies-help-define-genocide-in-online-documentary/\" title=\"阅读原文  [en]\">阅读原文  [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/12/02/10160/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E7%93%9C%E5%9C%B0%E9%A9%AC%E6%8B%89%EF%BC%9A%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8A%E7%BA%AA%E5%BD%95%E7%89%87%E9%80%8F%E8%BF%87%E5%B9%B8%E5%AD%98%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%81%E8%AF%8D%E6%9D%A5%E7%95%8C%E5%AE%9A%E7%A7%8D%E6%97%8F%E5%B1%A0%E6%9D%80&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F02%2F10160%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><s